Program_Title: Mary Kay Henry's Holiday Message to Members

Headlines: SEIU President Mary Kay Henry's video message to members this holiday season.

Text: for many hard-working families this season is filled with uncertainty
but i know together through our union we can bring out the best in each other and
rely on each other to face a future where if each of us rise to a new level
of leadership anything's possible i'll look forward to working with you in the
new year around our fight for a new economy happy holidays
enjoy your family and rest up because we got some work to do in the new year
